    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 3.4L flat-six featuring an integrated dry-sump lubrication system and VarioCam Plus timing. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox, offering short-throw precision and a direct mechanical connection to the pavement. The mid-engine architecture ensures a neutral polar moment of inertia, further enhanced by a recent suspension refresh including upgraded dampers and sway bar end links. The cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump and low-temp thermostat to ensure thermal stability during spirited runs. Cosmetically honest with minor road-derived patina, the vehicle is mechanically sorted, exhibiting zero vacuum leaks and a clean DME over-rev report.",
